snippet.title: maybe : Interactive Stories | Lady in Armour Ep 1 [Main Story]
snippet.description:
You took the path of chivalry to avenge your family. Just when you thought you failed your revenge and died, you are sent back to the time you lived as the Earl's daughter. Will you be able to protect your loved ones this time?
